From 294be8589cdf16ae62f68267302aafb20fd76785 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Imanol-Mikel Barba Sabariego <imanol@imanolbarba.net>
Date: Tue, 7 Jul 2026 22:40:27 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 1/9] Migrating to V2 API

getConfigValue and addConfigValue are deprecated

addConfigValueV2 creates a shared pointer that is updated dynamically by Hyprland everytime the config is reloaded, so we don't even need to keep track/update the copies
---
 src/Globals.hpp  | 143 +++++++++++++++++++++---------
 src/Input.cpp    |  40 ++++-----
 src/Layout.cpp   |  14 +--
 src/Overview.cpp |  18 ++--
 src/Render.cpp   |  72 +++++++--------
 src/main.cpp     | 223 ++++++++++++-----------------------------------
 6 files changed, 227 insertions(+), 283 deletions(-)

